A new version is out. Starting dialogue of scenario The Path of Revenge was improved, the enemy in the scenario gets more hitpoints on normal and hard. Enemies in scenario Return of the Orcs now have villages closer to their castles at start now. There is now a reminder of the objective of scenario Flight if one is taking too long to complete it and the turn limit was lowered to 12. Scenario An Exercise was renamed to An Unexpected Obstacle. Jolla now always has the illuminates ability in scenario March to the East, the starting dialogue was tweaked to take into account whether she and Lemyr have the ability or not.